PO_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/3_11.png?v=1763437346"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-4b7b8d79-4771-44da-94d1-51a0528b926b.gif"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/3_11.png?v=1763437346"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjPk9bJpvM_text","label":"ggjPk9bJpvM_text","default":"3. Sensitive Skin Friendly"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUrpHf4v9e_text","label":"ggUrpHf4v9e_text","default":"<p>If you have sensitive skin like me, finding something gentle but effective can be tough. That’s why I’m so excited about our mask—it’s made with all-natural ingredients that are super gentle but still work wonders. And in winter, when sensitive skin gets even drier and more reactive, this mask is a lifesaver. So many people with sensitive skin love how it gives that glass-skin effect without irritation or redness. It’s a total game-changer.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/4_12.png?v=1763437345"},{"type":"html","id":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-3af9d15b-e2f8-4ca4-b09b-b57ae744e609.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/4_12.png?v=1763437345"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQPtwZzMvG_text","label":"ggQPtwZzMvG_text","default":"4. Scientifically Proven Ingredients"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxpEEAWkOo_text","label":"ggxpEEAWkOo_text","default":"<p>When it